{
  "id": "69c63919ec692a1fa9058b2d",
  "title": "Cosenseのベクトル検索",
  "created": 1774598427,
  "updated": 1774600722,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69c63919ec692a1fa9058b2d",
      "text": "Cosenseのベクトル検索",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774598427,
      "updated": 1774598427
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6391a000000000005ee4d",
      "text": "from [2026/03/26] [倉下忠憲.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774598427,
      "updated": 1774598441
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6391a000000000005ee4f",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/b71a280306b8c9b2af573cdd5f4b138b]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774598427,
      "updated": 1774598427
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6391a000000000005ee50",
      "text": "　一行目がすぐに表示されて、ごくわずかに遅れて二行目以下が表示された",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774598427,
      "updated": 1774598427
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6391a000000000005ee51",
      "text": "　一行目は通常の検索だけども、二行目以下は[あいまい検索]ですらない",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774598427,
      "updated": 1774598602
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6391a000000000005ee52",
      "text": "　\tどんなロジックで選択されているのだろうか（手帳、とかシステムが入っているのはわかるがそうでないものもある）",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774598427,
      "updated": 1774598427
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6391a000000000005ee53",
      "text": "　\t[assets/index.js解析勢]の出番だ[Mijikko.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774598427,
      "updated": 1774598427
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6391a000000000005ee54",
      "text": "　！？ほんとだ[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774598427,
      "updated": 1774598427
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6391a000000000005ee55",
      "text": "　 > [@shokai https://twitter.com/shokai/status/2036097720394399891]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774598427,
      "updated": 1774600694
    },
    {
      "id": "69c641f7000000000075b713",
      "text": "  > [https://gyazo.com/2d27d1249ef5cc750a45be606bf74d50]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774600694,
      "updated": 1774600719
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6391a000000000005ee56",
      "text": " すごい👀[caki.icon][mtane0412.icon][yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774598427,
      "updated": 1774598484
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6391a000000000005ee57",
      "text": " 何らかの類似度を記事の中身を見て計算してるのかなあ[基素.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774598427,
      "updated": 1774598427
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6391a000000000005ee58",
      "text": "  直接記事内に書いていない言葉でもタイトルがサジェストされる",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774598427,
      "updated": 1774598427
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6391a000000000005ee59",
      "text": "  記事の意味と検索キーワードの意味の類似度が高いものがヒットする、みたいな",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774598427,
      "updated": 1774598427
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6391a000000000005ee5a",
      "text": "\tとりあえずembeddings（[埋め込みベクトル]？）つくってるのは読めた[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774598427,
      "updated": 1774598457
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6391a000000000005ee5b",
      "text": "\t\t[https://gyazo.com/24b7f3bd40317fc1fca12ce7cef07e94]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774598427,
      "updated": 1774598427
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6391a000000000005ee5c",
      "text": "　　GJ！[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774598427,
      "updated": 1774598427
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6391a000000000005ee5d",
      "text": "　　　そうなんじゃないかと思ったけどエビデンスが見つかってよかった",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774598427,
      "updated": 1774598427
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6391a000000000005ee5e",
      "text": "　[api/pages/:projectname/search/vector/titles?q=:query]で検索できる[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774598427,
      "updated": 1774598427
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6391a000000000005ee5f",
      "text": "　 $ await (await fetch(`/api/pages/${scrapbox.Project.name}/search/vector/titles?q=${encodeURIComponent(\"システム手帳\")}`)).json()",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774598427,
      "updated": 1774598427
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6391a000000000005ee60",
      "text": "　 使っているのは[Atlas Vector Search]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774598427,
      "updated": 1774598427
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6391a000000000005ee61",
      "text": "　  [MongoDB Vector Search | MongoDB https://www.mongodb.com/products/platform/atlas-vector-search]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774598427,
      "updated": 1774598471
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6391a000000000005ee62",
      "text": "　 すごい[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774598427,
      "updated": 1774598427
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6391a000000000005ee63",
      "text": "　　やったー[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774598427,
      "updated": 1774598427
    },
